+
+Originally ripped off from L<Test::Harness>.
+
+=head1 SEE ALSO
+
+L<TAP::Object>,
+L<TAP::Parser>,
+L<TAP::Parser::Iterator>,
+L<TAP::Parser::IteratorFactory>,
+
+=cut
+
